        <text>
            <body>
                
                    <p>Ego <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324599" xml:id="d1e140368" corresp="Manassès de Bar-sur-Seine, évêque de Langres (1179-1193)">.M., Dei gratia
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#317574" xml:id="d1e140370" corresp="Langres (Haute-Marne, Langres)">Lingonensis</placeName> episcopus</persName>, litteris nostris
                        sigillatis notum facio de gage<lb n="2" break="no" />ria <persName key="d1e14526" xml:id="d1e140376">Reginaudi filii vicecomitis de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324349" xml:id="d1e140378" corresp="Quincy-le-Vicomte (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Quinceio</placeName>
                        </persName>, quia predictus <persName key="d1e14532" xml:id="d1e140381">Reginaudus</persName> po<lb n="3" break="no" />suit in vadimonium pro
                            XX<hi rend="superscript">ti</hi> libris de divionensisbus fratribus
                        ecclesie Sancte Marie de <lb n="4" />
                        <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e140391" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneto</orgName> censam
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324335" xml:id="d1e140394" corresp="La Villeneuve-les-Convers,La-Villeneuve-les-Convers (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Noville
                            Montis</placeName>, scilicet .IIII<hi rend="superscript">or</hi>
                        sestarios frumenti, .IIII<hi rend="superscript">or</hi>. sestarios <lb n="5" /> avene, .X. solidos divionensis monete. Hoc laudaverunt in presentia
                        nostra <lb n="6" />
                        <persName key="d1e14538" xml:id="d1e140407">Margarita</persName> mater ejus,
                            <persName key="d1e14545" xml:id="d1e140410">Odo</persName> frater ejus.
                        Quando predictus <persName key="d1e14551" xml:id="d1e140413">.R.</persName>
                        vel aliquis suorum <lb n="7" /> fratrum voluerit redimere, redimet predictis
                            .XX<hi rend="superscript">ti</hi> libris acceptis, in ea<lb n="8" break="no" />dem valitudine in qua tunc erant. Tunc vero quinquaginta
                        solidi illius monete <lb n="9" /> marcam valebant. Et si de moneta illa
                        fieret contentio, pro .L. solidis mar<lb n="10" break="no" />ca solveretur.
                        Inde testes sunt : <persName key="d1e14557" xml:id="d1e140428">.R. abbas de
                                <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283938" xml:id="d1e140430" corresp="abbaye Saint-Jean de Réôme ou Moutier-Saint-Jean (440 -)">Monasterio Sancti
                                Johannis</orgName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e14563" xml:id="d1e140433">.G. decanus <lb n="11" /> de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324487" xml:id="d1e140437" corresp="Montbard (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Monte
                                Barro</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e14569" xml:id="d1e140441">magister Erembertus
                            de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324355" xml:id="d1e140443" corresp="Rougemont (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Rubeo
                                Monte</placeName>
                        </persName>. Quicumque contra hoc quod de pre<lb n="12" break="no" />fata
                        gageria scripsimus ire voluerit, anatema sit.<figure rend="trait" />
                    </p>
                
            </body>
